      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"5. MY GIRL AUBREE has put together back-to-back placings, the latest when 2.5 lengths away in third over 1308m at this track (Dirt) when she was in the firing line all the way. Well placed and there is no reason she cannot find winning ways. 4. LADY DELILAH is a 19-start maiden who finished fourth at her most recent outing over 1308m at this track (Dirt). Well placed on this occasion and gets her chance to break the ice. 3. SHE'S BANKABLE went forward over 1308m at this track (Dirt) last time but found a couple better. Sure to give a great sight. 1. NO RESERVE stepped out for her debut over 1106m at Saratoga (Dirt) back on June 8 and finished fifth, beaten 12 lengths. Open to improvement and can feature.\",\"runners\":[5,4,3,1],\"exclusive\":false}",
